<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd" identifier="question-5-variant-1" title="Comparación de tiempos de carrera - Variante 1" adaptive="false" time-dependent="false">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la tabla adjunta se presenta el tiempo que demoraron los atletas de una carrera de 100 metros planos en llegar a la meta.</p>
    <div>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Atleta</th>
            <th>Tiempo en segundos</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Andrés</td>
            <td>11,05</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Bruno</td>
            <td>11,55</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Carlos</td>
            <td>11,50</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>David</td>
            <td>11,45</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Esteban</td>
            <td>11,60</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices="1" response-identifier="RESPONSE">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuáles de los atletas llegaron después de Carlos?</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">Andrés y David</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">Bruno y Esteban</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">Solo Esteban</qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">Ninguno de los atletas</qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing template="https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml"/>
</qti-assessment-item>